The link maintains excellent SLA compliance (99.99% of time in Excellent/Good categories), indicating no ongoing performance bottlenecks.

**Conclusion**
This link is significantly over-provisioned and should be downgraded to a target of 23 Mbps for substantial cost savings without impacting performance.
